reviewText:
One of the best Point-n-Click games that I've ever played with charismatic characters and an involving history.

+Creative and attractive history with hilarious characters;
+Great stylization of the level design that fits with the game's idea;
+Well thinked and entertaining puzzles;
+Every single soundtrack fits in it's own part of the game perfectly.

-Sometimes the player is forced to do some things for the history continues, even against his will;
-Inexperienced players in Point-n-Click games usually get stuck in some parts.

